From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Remove Google Update

Disables Google's background update service.

---
 chrome/browser/google/google_update_settings.cc | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/chrome/browser/google/google_update_settings.cc b/chrome/browser/google/google_update_settings.cc
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/chrome/browser/google/google_update_settings.cc
+++ b/chrome/browser/google/google_update_settings.cc
@@ -20,6 +20,10 @@

 namespace google_update {

+bool GetCollectStatsConsent() {
+  return false;
+}
+
 bool IsGoogleUpdateEnabled() {
   return false;
 }
--
2.40.0
